This etc/raft code has been modified to add following features:

1. multi-raft support.
2. snapshot manager.
3. merged and compressed heartbeat message.
4. check down replica.
5. single raft's panic is allowed, detectable.
6. new wal implementation.
7. export more run status.
8. implementation batch commit.

